Keyword Magic Tool

Find millions of keyword suggestions for your SEO.

Examples:
  • loans
  • movies
  • how to buy audible books
AI-powered feature

Enter a topic and get your list of best keywords for you

Get fresh data

Semrush database shows you the most recent data and trends at all times.

Work with topical groups

Research keywords in thematic subgroups and exclude irrelevant groups from your search.

Keyword Research with Semrush — it’s easy
as one, two, three!

  1. Validate topics by the most important metrics in Keyword Overview
  2. Generate the most effective keyword ideas for optimization in Keyword Magic Tool
  3. Save all of your research in one place in Keyword Strategy Builder

Find your next best keyword idea!

Examples:
